2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves optimization techniques and linearization methods, which are commonly used in information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the design and optimization of a complex system, which is a common theme in systems and control. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper deals with the deployment of distributed units and cloud units, which is a distributed computing problem. 
5. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper does not directly deal with hardware architecture, but it does involve the design and optimization of a complex system, which can be related to hardware architecture.
